DTSTAMP:20260626T212248Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260717
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260718
SUMMARY:Deadline: Beautiful Bizarre Art Prize 2026
DESCRIPTION:International\, non-acquisitive art prize across seven categori
 es including a dedicated Digital Art Award\, with cash prizes and a San Fr
 ancisco gallery exhibition. Grand Prize is $10\,000\, with category awards
  and over $76\,000 in total cash and prizes. ELIGIBILITY: open internation
 ally with no geographic restriction\; all static media\; includes an Emerg
 ing Artist Award. NOTE: there is a $40 entry fee per submission.\n\nOrgani
 sation: Beautiful Bizarre Magazine\nLocation: Worldwide (exhibition in San
  Francisco\, USA)\nAward: Grand Prize $10\,000 plus category awards (e.g. 
 Imaginative Realism $5\,000) and a dedicated Digital Art Award and Emergin
 g Artist Award\; $76\,000+ total in cash and prizes. NOTE: $40 entry fee p
 er submission.\nDuration: Annual prize (exhibition follows)\n\nMore: https
 ://beautifulbizarreartprize.art/enter-beautiful-bizarre-art-prize/
URL:https://beautifulbizarreartprize.art/enter-beautiful-bizarre-art-prize/
LOCATION:Worldwide (exhibition in San Francisco\, USA)
END:VEVENT
