 rize)
DESCRIPTION:Seasonal international art prize from Biafarin (a Canadian arti
 st-management platform)\, running a juried online group exhibition with ca
 sh grants\, magazine/catalogue features\, ARTSY presentation\, and up to 1
 0 solo online exhibitions. CASH GRANTS (modest): Major Grant CAD 500 (1 ar
 tist)\; Merit Grant CAD 250 each (4 artists)\; Recognition Grant CAD 100 e
 ach (10 artists). Plus up to 10 Honorable Mention certificates and various
  promotion benefits. ELIGIBILITY: open to all visual artists worldwide age
 d 18+\, any 2D/3D medium (painting\, drawing\, illustration\, printmaking\
 , photography\, digital art\, fiber\, sculpture\, mixed media)\; originals
  only\, no copies/derivatives. SUBMISSION: free of charge. NOTE ON FEE: on
 ly SELECTED artists pay a fixed USD 50 selection fee (USD 40 early-bird) t
 o participate in the exhibition\; most selected artists pay this fee and d
 o not receive a cash grant. Money-back guarantee on the selection fee unti
 l the official exhibition opening day. Up to 10 artworks per artist\; max 
 2 may be selected. Deadline 9 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Biafarin\nLocati
 on: Online (Canadian organisation\; worldwide submissions and online exhib
 ition)\nAward: Cash grants per artist: Major Grant CAD 500 (1 artist)\; Me
 rit Grant CAD 250 each (4 artists\, total CAD 1\,000 pool)\; Recognition G
 rant CAD 100 each (10 artists\, total CAD 1\,000 pool). NOTE: submission i
 s free\, but SELECTED ARTISTS PAY a USD 50 selection fee (USD 40 early bir
 d) to participate in the exhibition. Money-back guarantee on the selection
  fee until exhibition opening day.\nDuration: Online group exhibition 1 Ju
 l - 30 Sep 2026 (3 months)\; up to 10 selected for separate 2-month online
  solo exhibitions\n\nMore: https://www.biafarin.com/boaps
